creator: The Falcon Spade
descriptionHtml:
Control a ball by avoiding hazards while moving along the Fairway
With ramps, slopes and side-grounds at your aid, you’re able to strategize ways in which you can reach the end of the level whilst avoiding collision with any laid-out obstacles.

-- --

Similar to the game of golf, the game has levels which vary in difficulty. The experience requires strategic application and estimation, which when combined make for a interactive, challenging casual game.

Game Features:
- Engaging game play: Attempt to anticipate the directional bounce of the ball in advance
- Variant progression: Some later levels pose less of a challenge than others
- Multiple solutions: Each level can be approached and beaten in a different way (there's no set way of reaching the end), however some approaches are a sure fire way to collide with hazards
- Simplicity: Fairway is a hyper-casual game presenting a substantial dose of an addictive challenge.
- Head-up Display: Estimate your progression through each level by monitoring the number on the HUD. Levels end between 4000 and 5000
descriptionShort: Control your player ball by avoiding hazards while moving along the Fairway.
